    Create a new phylogenetic flow path object (pfp)

    pfp.Rd

    Create a new phylogenetic flow path object (pfp)

    Usage

    pfp(x = list())

pf_is_pfp(x)

    Arguments

    x

    • For pfp(): A list of nodes (integer) the path passes through

    • For is_pfp(): An object to test.

    Value

    A pfp object

    Examples

    pfp(ape::nodepath(ape::rtree(100)))
